<li id="cite_note-21"><b><a href="#cite_ref-21" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.iwpr.net/?p=crs&amp;s=f&amp;o=161411&amp;apc_state=henicrs2002" class="external free" title="http://www.iwpr.net/?p=crs&amp;s=f&amp;o=161411&amp;apc_state=henicrs2002" rel="nofollow">http://www.iwpr.net/?p=crs&amp;s=f&amp;o=161411&amp;apc_state=henicrs2002</a> Abkhazia: Cultural Tragedy Revisited</li>
<li id="cite_note-22"><b><a href="#cite_ref-22" title="">^</a></b> <i>Al-Hayat</i>, January 13, 2001</li>
<li id="cite_note-23"><b><a href="#cite_ref-23" title="">^</a></b> <i>Middle East Report</i>, 219 Summer 2001</li>
